cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.IT, cs.CY 

This paper is about a text steganography method, which involves hiding information within a text. This topic is closely related to computer security (cs.CR) and machine learning (cs.LG), as well as natural language processing (cs.CL) and information theory (cs.IT). Additionally, the use of Markov chains is a common technique in cyber security (cs.CY), which further supports the inclusion of this category.
